S_{\mathrm{MCM}}\left(\mathbf{x}^{\prime};\mathcal{\mathcal{V}}_{\mathrm{in}},\mathcal{T},\mathbb{Z}\right)=\operatorname*{max}_{i}\frac{e^{s_{i}\left(\mathbf{x}^{\prime}\right)/\tau}}{\sum_{j=1}^{K}e^{s_{j}\left(\mathbf{x}^{\prime}\right)/\tau}}
