$$
S_{\mathrm{CLIPN}}(x)=\sum_{j=1}^{C}\frac{e^{s_{i,j}^{n o}(x)/\tau}}{e^{s_{i,j}(x)/\tau}+e^{s_{i,j}^{n o}(x)/\tau}}\cdot\frac{e^{s_{i,j}(x)/\tau}}{\sum_{k=1}^{C}e^{s_{i,k}(x)/\tau}}
$$

$$
S_{\mathrm{NegLabel}}(x)=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{K}e^{s_{i}(x)/\tau}}{\sum_{i=1}^{K}e^{s_{i}(x)/\tau}+\sum_{j=1}^{M}e^{s_{j}^{\mathrm{neg}}(x)/\tau}}
$$

$$
